Test Case 2: Invalid Email Address
Test Case ID: TC002

Test Case Title: Verify login with an invalid email address.

Test Steps:

Navigate to the Trendyol login page.
Enter an invalid email address (e.g., "invalidemail@domain.com") in the username input field.
Enter a valid password ("Sude1trendyol") in the password input field.
Click on the login button.
Expected Result: The user should not be logged in, and an appropriate error message should be displayed indicating that the email address is invalid.

Actual Result: done

Status: (Pass/Fail)
